# âœ… **CSS (styles.css)**

```css
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  padding: 30px;
}

.card {
  background: #fff;
  width: 95%;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 20px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* Left side form */
.form-section {
  flex: 2;
}

.row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.col {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

label {
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 5px;
}

select {
  padding: 6px;
}

/* Middle buttons */
.button-section {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 15px;
}

button {
  background: #0078ff;
  color: #fff;
  border: none;
  padding: 8px 14px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

button:hover {
  opacity: 0.85;
}

/* Vertical line */
.line {
  width: 2px;
  height: 100%;
  background: gray;
}

/* Right side */
.right-content {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* Mobile Responsive */
@media (max-width: 850px) {
  .card {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .line {
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
  }
}
```

